==================================================
CURRENT WORK — Curated track refresh
Date: 2026-04-11
==================================================

==================================================
GOAL
==================================================

Update the Blind 75 and NeetCode 150 track manifests after expanding the
LeetCode provider registry.

Keep the provider registry free-only. Do not create track references to problems
that are unavailable in registry/providers/leetcode.json.

==================================================
WHAT CHANGED
==================================================

1. TRACK UPDATER

  Added:
    scripts/update_curated_tracks.mjs

  The script:
    - defines canonical Blind 75 and NeetCode 150 slug lists
    - validates there are no duplicate slugs
    - filters each list against registry/providers/leetcode.json
    - writes registry/tracks/blind75.json
    - writes registry/tracks/neetcode150.json
    - updates track checksums in registry/index.json

2. BLIND 75 TRACK

  Updated:
    registry/tracks/blind75.json

  Canonical count:
    75

  Available in free provider registry:
    70

  Omitted unavailable slugs:
    graph-valid-tree
    number-of-connected-components-in-an-undirected-graph
    alien-dictionary
    meeting-rooms
    meeting-rooms-ii

  Checksum:
    sha256:4e67f788c5dc2a600a9d2e639eabbbbcdfa4c51b12aae49a5b4a2ce6cb0a4b8d

