==================================================
VERIFICATION
==================================================

  jq empty registry/index.json registry/tracks/blind75.json registry/tracks/neetcode150.json
  node --check scripts/update_curated_tracks.mjs

Reference validation:
  registry/tracks/blind75.json      count 70, missingRefs 0, badOrders 0, dups 0
  registry/tracks/neetcode150.json  count 143, missingRefs 0, badOrders 0, dups 0

==================================================
DESIGN DECISION
==================================================

Do not add paid-only LeetCode metadata just to make the tracks reach their full
canonical counts.

Reason:
  The local provider registry is currently intentionally free-only. A track entry
  that points at a missing provider problem would break sync/UI behavior, while
  adding paid-only provider entries would violate the current registry policy.
